media.altText:
"Shattered from within”
City 15 Connections - Ether - Shattered from within - xyz1
rubbing, drawing and digital collage
#love #hope #fear #artoftheday #sketch #digitalcollage #nft #nftcollection #drawing #photography #creatives #brokeninside #depression
Charli098 explores the interplay between the familiar and unfamiliar, seen and unseen, and tactile and digital using rubbing, drawing, and collage techniques to capture the essence of the urban environment. They incorporate digital tools into their practice to create hybrid forms that blur the boundaries between physical and virtual. Recycled materials play a central role in their work, reflecting the rhythms and textures of contemporary life. The artist's aim is to understand and connect to what they see, producing internal philosophical questions about identity and the environment.

Poster saying 'many people are bounced around the system for years trying to get a diagnosis and are often left with no support and nowhere to turn'
A poster saying 'sadly people with Tourette Syndrome are over 4 times more likely to die by suicide. We would like to dedicate this animation to those who are no longer with us'
